    "skill": "Command of Evidence — Textual",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "passage": "\"Often Rebuked, Yet Always Back Returning\" is an 1846 poem by Emily Brontë. The poem conveys the speaker's determination to\nexperience the countryside around her: ______",
