    "passage": "Sense and Sensibility is an 1811 novel by Jane Austen. In the novel, Austen describes Marianne Dashwood's ability to persuade\nothers of the rightness of her artistic judgments, as is evident when Marianne visits with John Willoughby, a potential suitor: ______",
